'''A_CloseShotgun2'''

(no parameters)

Plays the sound "weapons/sshotc" and calls [[A_ReFire]].  This is equivalent to doing the following:
     SHT2 H 6 
     {
         [[A_StartSound]] ("weapons/sshotc", CHAN_WEAPON);
         [[A_ReFire]]();
     }
